      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable, functional option for those who prioritize utility over perfection. While the car runs and drives well, the exterior shows some noticeable scratches and minor dings consistent with its age, and the interior has some wear on the upholstery. It has been regularly serviced, though it may require some minor cosmetic attention or small repairs in the near future to bring it back to top shape.",
