    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to offer this peerless example of automotive engineering, maintained to an exacting standard that mirrors its original delivery state. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the sophisticated collector or enthusiast to acquire a specimen characterized by an unblemished aesthetic and flawless mechanical performance. Every surface and component reflects meticulous stewardship, ensuring that this offering stands as a definitive benchmark for its class.",
