      "description": "Presenting an unparalleled example of automotive excellence, this vehicle is offered in impeccable, showroom-grade condition. Every aspect of this specimen\u2014from its flawless exterior finish to its pristine, high-caliber interior\u2014reflects a standard of preservation rarely encountered in the secondary market. Meticulously maintained and mechanically beyond reproach, this vehicle represents a premier acquisition for the discerning enthusiast who demands uncompromising quality and aesthetic perfection. We invite you to experience a vehicle that sets the benchmark for its class.",
      "price": 46500.0,
